drm/i915/rkl: Handle new DPCLKA_CFGCR0 layout

RKL uses a slightly different bit layout for the DPCLKA_CFGCR0 register.

v2:
 - Fix inverted mask application when updating ICL_DPCLKA_CFGCR0
 - Checkpatch style fixes

